text: <!channel>: Reminder we have a hackathon starting this wed.  It's virtual so should be easy to 'attend'.  You can get something useful out of a couple hours each day rather than committing to multiple days away from your main work.  The link <@U0YQQRNU8> gave above is for 1 of 2 suggested projects.  The second is for an identity aspect of sawtooth (<http://lists.hyperledger.org/pipermail/hyperledger-stl/2016-June/000002.html>).
